reviewText:

My brother got this tape a little after I finished high school. Watched it so much that the part with Christy Thom nearly faded out! Imagine how bad I felt when my dumb brother told me one day he lost it!!!! Then over fifteen years later, I come across your ad on amazon. THANK YOU- THANK YOU- THANK YOU-THANK YOU!!!!

Best of Samantha Dorman,Rocking Carrie Yazel, Cuter than cute Christy Thom, Stacy Arthur sings city boys crazy, (I'm running out of breath). To complete the Darling Dozen: Wendy Kaye, Christina Leardini, Julie Clarke, Saskia Linssen, Corinna Harney, Tonja Christiansen, Cheryl Bachman, and that wrench swinging tomboy Wendy Hamilton! Don't leave you computer without this!

The Video Calendars started in 1987.  This is the 1st of these so the calendars had a 5 year head start is one reason that series probably won out.  I wish this series did because then you'd have a complete history of playmates from that time forward instead of the near complete record you get on the calendars usually repeating the PMOY 2 consecutive years but on with the review.

Tonja Christensen is great though her 1st clip has some overly grainy footage.
Samantha Doorman was okay just not my personal taste.
Julie Clark is great but I'm not a fan of underwater clips.
Carrie Yazel is cool but I like her baking footage elsewhere better.
Stacy Arthur does her own music video which is cool.  She's okay.
Christy Thom is a cutie & seems very fun.
Saskia Linsen has a hairstile I don't care for but nice breasts.
Christina Leardini is one of the best ever.  She has better footage out there.
Wendy Kaye is one of the best ever.  The 4th of July clip is very good.
Cheryl Backman has a great body, very cute girl overall.
Wendy Hamilton actually has a somewhat longer than her usual "boy" hairstyle here which is nice.
Corinna Harney is cool but there's better footage out there.

A nice recap of a good year of playmates.

Playboy Video Playmate Review 1992 is 56 minutes long and was released on video on November 7, 1991. This is not a Playboy video calendar. This is a review of Playmates from the year 1991. The review seems to have more nudity then the calendars that I have review in the past. The only person who seems to be afraid to express herself is Saskia Linssen\Playmate of the Month for June, 1991. Below are the Playmates that they appeared in the order of the video.

Tonja Marie Christensen\Playmate of the Month for November, 1991-Flashes breasts, then topless, and then nude first half. In the second scene there is full nudity.
Samantha Dorman\Playmate of the Month for September, 1991-Nude most of the time
Julie Clarke\Playmate of the Month for March, 1991-Jull nudity in swimming pool scene, some nudity in second segment
Carrie Jean Yazel\Playmate of the Month for May, 1991-Topless 15% of the time first segment, very little nudity second half
Stacy Arthur\Playmate of the Month for January, 1991-Sang in music video and showed some breast first half, full nudity most of the time second half.
Cristy Thom\Playmate of the Month for February, 1991(Playmate of the Year in 1992 for the Dutch edition of Playboy)-A little topless at times first half. Second half of segment, there is full nudity.
Saskia Linssen\Playmate of the Month for June, 1991-Total video consists of 5% nudity
Christina Leardini\Playmate of the Month for April, 1991-Some nudity first half, full nudity second half.
Wendy Kaye\Playmate of the Month for July, 1991-Some nudity first half, full nudity second half
Cheryl Bachman\Playmate of the Month for October, 1991-Very brief nudity first half, more nudity second half
Wendy Hamilton\Playmate of the Month for December, 1991-Nude 50% of the time first segment, topless, and then nude in second segment.
Corinna Harney\Playmate of the Month for August, 1991 (Playboy's Playmate of the Year 1992)-Quick topless and nude takes first half, mainly nude second half.

Playboy Video Playmate Review 1992 gets a B+.
